<item>
            <title>[HBASE-9835] Define C interface of HBase Client APIs</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-9835</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Creating this as a sub task of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-1015&quot; title=&quot;HBase Native Client Library&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-1015&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-1015&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; to define Define C language interface of HBase Client synchronous APIs.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
